'''星州郡'''（{{kor|諺=성주군|漢=星州郡|羅=Seongju gun|f=y}}）是位於[[大韓民國|大韓民國]][[慶尚北道|慶尚北道]]西南部的[[郡|郡]]，西界[[慶尚南道|慶尚南道]]，東界[[大邱廣域市|大邱廣域市]]。西有[[伽倻山|伽倻山]]，東有[[洛東江|洛東江]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=星州郡-基本概况|url=https://sj.go.kr/S0008/page.do?mnu_uid=2893&|access-date=2021-07-04|publisher=星州郡|language=zh|archive-date=2021-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210709182106/https://sj.go.kr/S0008/page.do?mnu_uid=2893&|dead-url=no}}</ref>面積616.16方公里，2009年人口44,987人。下分1邑、9面。

[[中部內陸高速公路|中部內陸高速公路]]經過該郡。第三套部署於美國以外的[[戰區高空防御飛彈|戰區高空防御飛彈]]（THAAD）系統裝設於此郡{{Translink|ko|초전면|草田面|草田面}}韶成里<ref>{{Cite web|title=全面开动：美韩部署萨德关键部分|url=https://www.dw.com/zh/%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E5%BC%80%E5%8A%A8%E7%BE%8E%E9%9F%A9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%90%A8%E5%BE%B7%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86/a-38594658|access-date=2021-07-04|date=2017-04-26|last=|first=|work=|publisher=[[德国之声|德国之声]]|language=zh|archive-date=2021-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210711015401/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E5%BC%80%E5%8A%A8%E7%BE%8E%E9%9F%A9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%90%A8%E5%BE%B7%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86/a-38594658|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=韩政府7日凌晨追加部署萨德发射车|url=http://cnnews.chosun.com/client/news/viw.asp?cate=c01&mcate=m1001&nNewsNumb=20170948374&nidx=|access-date=2021-07-04|date=2017-09-06|work=|publisher=[[朝鮮日報|朝鮮日報]]|language=zh|archive-date=2021-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210709184143/http://cnnews.chosun.com/client/news/viw.asp?cate=c01&mcate=m1001&nNewsNumb=20170948374&nidx=|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=[르포] 공사 제대로 못하는 사드기지…성주 소성리 마을회관 앞 '고요'|url=https://www.yna.co.kr/view/AKR20180327111500053|access-date=2021-07-04|date=2018-03-27|last=박순기|work=|publisher=[[韩联社|韩联社]]|language=ko|archive-date=2021-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210710235122/https://www.yna.co.kr/view/AKR20180327111500053|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=详讯：韩萨德基地运入建材等物资|url=https://cn.yna.co.kr/view/ACK20210525001600881|access-date=2021-07-04|date=2021-05-25|last=이정운|work=|publisher=[[韩联社|韩联社]]|language=zh|archive-date=2021-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210711180900/https://cn.yna.co.kr/view/ACK20210525001600881|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

